item.title: Anyone working on the new rs client? O_o?
item.dc:creator: @Lin Lin
item.description:
@Lin wrote:

[quote=“CoonHunter, post:6, topic:502049”][quote author=Fire capez link=topic=620277.msg4249375#msg4249375 date=1362253610]

Do you mean the RS07 client? Its nothing but a backup Jagex had from August 2007. Find out what revision it was back then and there ya go, you have the version they are on.

not strictly true it has been updated
[/quote]
I don’t play anything timescale related so i wouldn’t know. But still, its just an old client they are bringing new life to.[/quote]This. However, you might be better off using one of the ‘deobs’ people are bringing about. Some of them are equipped with XTEA dumpers which you’ll need for maps.
